	<description>
		<![CDATA[
		<div align="center">
			<div class="alert alert-success" style="background-color:#DFF0D8;border-color:#D6E9C6;color: #468847;padding: 1px 0;">
				
				<h3><a href="//www.joomlart.com/joomla/templates/ja-morgan">Creative multipurpose Joomla template for business - JA Morgan</a></h3>
				
				<h4><a href="//www.joomlart.com/joomla/templates/ja-morgan" title="">Home</a> | <a href="//joomlart.com/demo/#ja_morgan" title="">Demo</a> | <a href="//www.joomlart.com/documentation/joomla-templates/ja-morgan" title="">Document</a> | <a href="//pm.joomlart.com/browse/JAMORGAN" title="">Changelog</a></h4>

				<p>JA Morgan multipurpose Joomla template is a complete solution to quickly build beautiful websites for all kinds of businesses, corporate firms, and creative agencies & company.  Supports 4 homepage variations with different style, beautiful additional pages and impressive page elements.</p>

				<span style="color:#FF0000">Note: JA morgan requires T3 plugin to be installed and enabled.</span><p></p>
				<p>Copyright 2004 - 2019 <a href='http://www.joomlart.com/' title='Visit Joomlart.com!'>JoomlArt.com</a>.</p>
			</div>
			<style>table.adminform{width: 100%;}</style>
		</div>
		]]>
	</description>
